
---

### `.gitignore` for backend

Save this as `backend/.gitignore`:

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/

# Build output
dist/
build/

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
logs/
*.log

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

# OS / editor files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# Coverage
coverage/

# Temporary files
tmp/
temp/
